Marcellus recovers Helorus, Herbessus, and Megara. Pursued by Himilco with superior force. Retires to the camp before Syracuse. Himilco takes Agrigentum and Murgantia. Henna. L. Pinarius. Effect of his conduct on the other Sicilian towns, (xxxv—xxxix.)
